inblick in das Fach. Ganz besonderer Wert wird auf den reichhaltigen Übungsteil gelegt, der u.a. präzise Leseanleitungen für gezielt ausgesuchte Literatur weiterführenden Charakters gibt.  aThis book provides a detailed introduction to Romance linguistics, giving valuable information on 1) working techniques and tools, 2) the sub-disciplines of linguistics, and 3) Romance languages, thus linking theoretical reflection with practical skills. The book is divided into identically structured units (including working techniques, branches of linguistics, and language outlines) that provide a condensed introduction to the field. Particular focus is placed on the extensive exercise section.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aEinführung. 4aLinguistik. 4aRomanistik. 7aFOREIGN LANGUAGE STUDY / Romance Languages (Other).2bisacsh  aLinguistics.  aMethodology.  aRomance Studies.1 aPöll, Bernhard, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRainer, Franz, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2022z9783110993684oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831107554800 cprintz978311075531240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311075542840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110755428423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110755428/original  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSPb2022